# CSharpScript

**Inherits:** [Script](Script.md) **\<** [Resource](Resource.md) **\<** [RefCounted](RefCounted.md) **\<** [Object](Object.md)

A script implemented in the C# programming language, saved with the ``.cs`` extension (Mono-enabled builds only).

<!-- classref-introduction-group -->

## Description

This class represents a C# script. It is the C# equivalent of the [GDScript](GDScript.md) class and is only available in Mono-enabled Redot builds.
